<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fa" dir="rtl">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>ورود مشتری</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Vazirmatn:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg,#0d0f1b,#13172b,#141a33);
      font-family: Vazirmatn, sans-serif;
      color: #fff;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 30px 12px;
    }

    .card {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 520px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
      border-radius: 18px;
      padding: 24px;
      box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.45);
      backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
    }

    h1 { margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 26px; color: #7ec7ff; }
    p { margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 18px; opacity: .8; }

    label { display: block; margin-bottom: 8px; font-weight: 600; }
    input {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 12px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      color: #fff;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
      font-size: 15px;
    }

    input:focus { outline: 2px solid #6aa7ff; }

    button {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 14px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg,#3a8bff,#6aa7ff);
      border: none;
      border-radius: 14px;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: #0c1225;
      cursor: pointer;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 22px rgba(80,150,255,0.35);
      transition: .25s;
    }

    button:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); }

    .alert { padding: 12px; border-radius: 12px; margin-bottom: 14px; }
    .alert.error { background: rgba(255,80,80,0.18); border: 1px solid rgba(255,80,80,0.4); }

    .links { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-top: 10px; font-size: 14px; }
    .links a { color: #9ed5ff; text-decoration: none; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="card">
    <h1>ورود مشتری</h1>
    <p>شماره تماس و رمز ثبت‌شده را وارد کنید تا اطلاعات خود را مشاهده یا تکمیل نمایید.</p>

    <% if (error) { %>
      <div class="alert error"><%= error %></div>
    <% } %>

    <form action="/customer/login" method="POST">
      <label>شماره تماس</label>
      <input type="text" name="phone" required placeholder="0912...">

      <label>رمز عبور</label>
      <input type="password" name="password" required placeholder="******">

      <button type="submit">ورود</button>
    </form>

    <div class="links">
      <a href="/customer/create-account">حساب ندارید؟ ثبت‌نام</a>
      <a href="/">بازگشت به صفحه اصلی</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
